<p>Today it&#039;s all about answering your questions! Ok, maybe &lt;em&gt;one&lt;/em&gt; tip, but it&#039;s high time your questions got answered, and your two favorite geeks are just the right guys to do it! First it&#039;s two macOS Sierra questions, then it&#039;s onto APFS and the future of backups, including a query about choosing an external backup drive. This plus perhaps the aforementioned tip might just round out the show&#8230; or there might be more about Photos and HDR. Listen and find out!Note: Show notes are complete!</p>
